    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p><strong>This is a high-level overview of the different flows an inventory item will go through in RepairQ.</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787743/Inventory%20Management.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Control - f79824.png\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787743/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"InventoryManagementResources-CatalogItemManagement\">Catalog Item Management</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932329061\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creating a Catalog Item</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932624014\" rel=\"nofollow\">Catalog Management: Importing Catalog Items</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"InventoryManagementResources-Adding/StockingInventory\">Adding/Stocking Inventory</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932525994\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adding Inventory Into RepairQ</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1931018445\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Management: Adjusting Inventory Levels via Import</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932427416\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Order Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932460177\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Transfers: Requesting Items From Another Location</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"InventoryManagementResources-SellingInventory\">Selling Inventory</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1930494512\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creating a Quick Sale Ticket</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933508774\" rel=\"nofollow\">Repair Ticket Workflow</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933377756\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creating a Trade-In Ticket</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"InventoryManagementResources-SpecialWorkflows\">Special Workflows</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933279405\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creating a Refurbishment Ticket</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932525631\" rel=\"nofollow\">Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA) Tracking Overview</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932492924\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Management: Bulk-Edit Inventory Attributes</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1930494554\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Management: Tracking Non-inventoried Special Order Parts</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932624033\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Management: Tracking Inventoried Special Order Parts</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933672497\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inventory Management: Allowing for Backorder Inventory</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"InventoryManagementResources-Reporting\">Reporting</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934196750\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Valuation Snapshot</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934721039\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Usage</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934327847\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Expense</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934721025\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Orders</a></p></li></ul><p />",
